            <div data-seq="277263887" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">引子-行程单</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277252039">
            <br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;做为国家目前最南端的越冬旅游目的地，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>岛是值得一来再来的。这次，是第二次<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a><a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>游，与上一次的区别在于本次是环岛驾车自由行。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;本次行程安排如下（路书）：<br />
&nbsp;Day1&nbsp;&nbsp;飞抵<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>美兰机场，机场停车楼取网约<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>车去市区（25km），住<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12938.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海南" target="_blank">海南</a>太<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/22874.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="阳城" target="_blank">阳城</a>酒店（4星）。参观<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>骑楼、夜市、美食（<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11701.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="文昌" target="_blank">文昌</a>鸡饭必选），太<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/22874.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="阳城" target="_blank">阳城</a>大堂24小时书吧值得推荐；<br />
Day2&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/41342.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="琼海" target="_blank">琼海</a>温泉镇（105km），住<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/41342.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="琼海" target="_blank">琼海</a>官塘温泉休闲中心（四星）&nbsp;；&nbsp;&nbsp;游万泉河景区，泡温泉；<br />
Day3&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11616.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="万宁" target="_blank">万宁</a>石梅湾（75km），参观<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/52314.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="亚洲" target="_blank">亚洲</a>论坛会址或玉带湾看海，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/21804.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="博鳌" target="_blank">博鳌</a>镇中餐，下午驱车入住石梅湾威斯汀度假酒店（五星）；<br />
Day4、day5&nbsp;&nbsp;石梅湾-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a>（85km）&nbsp;&nbsp;入住<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196292.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海棠湾" target="_blank">海棠湾</a>9号（五星），游五指山景区、海滩休闲；<br />
Day6&nbsp;<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10030.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="三亚" target="_blank">三亚</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/196292.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海棠湾" target="_blank">海棠湾</a>-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62984.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="乐东" target="_blank">乐东</a>莺歌<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66313.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海盐" target="_blank">海盐</a>场&nbsp;（133km）；参观莺歌<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66313.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海盐" target="_blank">海盐</a>场，高速休息区午餐；&nbsp;&nbsp;莺歌海-<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>（296km），入住鲁能希尔顿（五星）；<br />
Day7&nbsp;酒店泡温泉，驱车去机场（19km），顺利返程。<br />

        </p>
            <div data-seq="277263764" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">海口（骑楼老街、文昌鸡饭、24小时书吧）</span></h2>
            </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_277272486" data-seq="277272487" data-pid="277272486" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8136842/277272486.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/2C/11/wKgBEFpEe4yAYzeNAAY_kSZjAjg42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/2C/11/wKgBEFpEe4yAYzeNAAY_kSZjAjg42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="277272486" alt="" />
        </a>
                    </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277272488">
            放飞
        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="277263947">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;早起的鸟儿有虫吃，搭乘早班航班飞<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>，此刻，登机口<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/62068.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="朝阳" target="_blank">朝阳</a>冉冉升起。<br />
&nbsp;经过2小时40分钟的飞行，准点降落<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>美兰机场。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;再次选择一嗨<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E7%A7%9F%E8%BD%A6" class="link" data-kw="租车"  target="_blank">租车</a>，机场新停车楼<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E5%8F%96%E8%BD%A6" class="link" data-kw="取车"  target="_blank">取车</a>，开启<a href="http://zuche.mafengwo.cn/jump_landing_page.php?keyword=%E8%87%AA%E9%A9%BE" class="link" data-kw="自驾"  target="_blank">自驾</a>之旅。去市区的路比上次好些，但拥堵更严重了。经济发展的必然结果是城市越来越拥堵。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;顺利抵达老城区的太<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/22874.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="阳城" target="_blank">阳城</a>酒店，没想到还是一家文化酒店，大堂有24小时开放的新华书店书吧，闲暇时光在书吧中打发，赶紧还是不错的。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;手机导航，逛<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10513.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="海口" target="_blank">海口</a>骑楼老街&nbsp;，品尝<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11701.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="文昌" target="_blank">文昌</a>鸡饭，满足一下味蕾。<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;入夜，在夜风中慢跑，&nbsp;感受骑楼老街夜之美。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_277272491" data-seq="277272492" data-pid="277272491" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/12938/scenery_8136842/277272491.html">
